OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlood scandal: 1 in 3      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finfected with HIV was a    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fchild                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Almost one out of every three people   
OL,6, infected with HIV through contaminated 
OL,7, NHS blood products in the 1970s and 80s
OL,8, was a child, research has found.       
OL,10,FAbout 380 children with haemophilia and
OL,11,Fother blood disorders are now thought  
OL,12,Fto have tested positive for the virus. 
OL,14,FThe new estimate was produced by the   
OL,15,Fpublic inquiry into the disaster, after
OL,16,Fa BBC News report into the scandal.    
OL,18,FIn August, the government agreed to pay
OL,19,Fsurvivors and the partners of those who
OL,20,Fdied compensation.                     
